會安排孟晚舟戴上電子腳鐐，透過GPS定位追蹤設備監視孟的行蹤。不過，檢控官指出，若該公司的電子腳鐐遭破壞，警報要在1分鐘後才會響起，且監控網絡有可能被黑客入侵。公司亦承認，以往曾有一名戴上電子腳鐐的保釋者成功潛逃。<br />\n<br />\n大批華裔民眾到庭旁聽孟晚舟案聆訊，《明報》加西版續報道，當中多人排隊入庭和在庭旁聽期間，沒有遵守法院規矩，包括以手機拍攝法院內部情況，庭警多番制止。另外，有人在庭上沒有關掉手機或調至靜音，其中一人的手機更兩度大聲響起《義勇軍進行曲》鈴聲。中午休庭時，部分人在法院門外大叫「釋放孟晚舟」。<br />\n</span></strong></span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"84994e88c82085770282e8a1c60cb256ac554055","tid":937561,"uid":96874,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T17:26:32.000Z","msg":"支那人真狡猾"},{"pid":"8373db178cc083540fe75071db8fe014c53b12ee","tid":937561,"uid":26506,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T17:27:38.000Z","msg":"Link?"},{"pid":"8290c071c4ec599ab20d896a4d88f521f11c8096","tid":937561,"uid":36178,"like":82,"dislike":0,"score":82,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T17:31:34.000Z","msg":"加拿大唔搞返次大型排華都唔洗旨意清到d癌 細胞"},{"pid":"aea54024ecbf5806ad13ed9200376b09a780a56e","tid":937561,"uid":24044,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8290c071c4ec599ab20d896a4d88f521f11c8096","tid":937561,"uid":36178,"like":82,"dislike":0,"score":82,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T17:31:34.000Z","msg":"加拿大唔搞返次大型排華都唔洗旨意清到d癌 細胞"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T17:36:20.000Z","msg":"要啦"},{"pid":"26eccb492a52057c58ea9ea3f2158d6ae3b78bba","tid":937561,"uid":131423,"like":36,"dislike":1,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T17:36:31.000Z","msg":"根本一保釋就走硬<br />\n美國佬唔放何志平咪醒囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f512307174f4055008eb5c31b927fe63ea259a7","tid":937561,"uid":138233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T17:40:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec48f5e8ce4d335683ff363b0545dbd732b1aa40","tid":937561,"uid":49203,"like":40,"dislike":1,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T17:49:45.000