" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f13c453b5a72fe43a9e020dfc7322d2a69a195e","tid":937561,"uid":155732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T01:40:03.000Z","msg":"孟晚舟<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> 想走</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n走你老母 坐監啦柒頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77a20d237e3a95a7a410eac9c7ce2f016d493b8a","tid":937561,"uid":155732,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"339347f235c06297723b029e2c1fd569a75bc2f5","tid":937561,"uid":61280,"like":50,"dislike":2,"score":48,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T17:23:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">建議方案：走犯一分鐘先識響！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong></span><br />\n<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n《明報》加西版報道，孟晚舟透過律師，向法庭提自聘兩間保安公司監視自己行蹤。兩間公司派員到庭解釋監視計劃，其中一間稱可提供「安全監控」服務，有從警或從軍經驗的人員全天候監控孟的行蹤，會分為3組，每8小時一崗，並會在數個城市和城鎮部分區域，劃定孟晚舟可「自由」活動的範圍。該公司的行政總裁又指願向法庭提交1000加元（約5838港元）保證金，倘若孟晚舟違反法庭要求，公司有權直接逮捕她。不過，公司承認過往從未試過為保釋者提供監視服務，且無法保證可防止孟晚舟逃脫。<br />\n<br />\n另一間保安公司則向法庭表示，會安排孟晚舟戴上電子腳鐐，透過GPS定位追蹤設備監視孟的行蹤。不過，檢控官指出，若該公司的電子腳鐐遭破壞，警報要在1分鐘後才會響起，且監控網絡有可能被黑客入侵。公司亦承認，以往曾有一名戴上電子腳鐐的保釋者成功潛逃。<br />\n<br />\n大批華裔民眾到庭旁聽孟晚舟案聆訊，《明報》加西版續報道，當中多人排隊入庭和在庭旁聽期間，沒有遵守法院規矩，包括以手機拍攝法院內部情況，庭警多番制止。另外，有人在庭上沒有關掉手機或調至靜音，其中一人的手機更兩度大聲響起《義勇軍進行曲》鈴聲。中午休庭時，部分人在法院門外大叫「釋放孟晚舟」。<br />\n</span></strong></span></blockquote>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T01:43:11.000Z","msg":"釋放孟晚舟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">放你老母</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">別讓她跑</span> 一定要搞死中共<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8c424a72ac61afa291c8ac7294b7090ca4339c0","tid":937561,"uid":155732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"158823c13a81806b68bf3560863dcf61f8d118f2","tid":937561,"uid":82929,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"991f4efe4e0ce18822c6352e8eed2186536c5138","tid":937561,"uid":14918,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T16:29:25.000Z","msg":"仲要防中共動用黑社會來却獄"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T22:35:45.000Z","msg":"我都覺溫哥華大把華人組織幫中共做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T01:45:25.000Z","msg":"美國要派啲SWAT去<br />\n帶重型武器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcfba3a6a530c8a166ef4ba9279749d14d3dd0fb","tid":937561,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T01:47:01.000Z","msg":"全世界得侵侵做到野， 成班垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d82bdad44ee9eb730c3ca0dcd5675b6947f6ce9","tid":937561,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a4ec95e6c95935e1774802f4a0f52f297488530","tid":937561,"uid":34869,"like":764,"dislike":1,"score":763,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T15:43:38.000Z","msg":"加拿大人終於比人發現滲透得好嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T01:50:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"806eb91e19553abc5c8ce5d51b2cada239f